trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection"></xref> class.
The default constructor initializes the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection> to an empty list.
trans-unit.target: 默认构造函数初始化<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection>为空列表。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection"></xref> class by using a list of workflow track points.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection"></xref>类使用的工作流跟踪点的列表。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection> is initialized to contain the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> objects specified in `points`.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection>初始化后将包含<xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint>中指定的对象`points`。</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPoint> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowTrackPointCollection>

trans-unit.source: points is a null reference ( in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: points为空引用 ( 在 Visual Basic 中)。
